            <lg xml:id="TK759">
<l>ceyka poruḷaic ceṟunar cerukkaṟukku</l>
<l>meḵkataṉiṟ kūriya til</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Accumulate wealth it will destroy the arrogance of (your) foes there is no weapon sharper than it.</l>
